The brand new SST Energy Seltzer’s from @Performix are a key essential for these late night sessions⚡️

A rejuvenating, light flavor with 0 Sugar, 0 Calories, and 300mg caffeine 

The seltzer’s are now in GNC and to celebrate- Performix and GNC are teaming up to giveaway $10,000! Head to @sstenergy to learn more about the $10k giveaway they’re hosting from 5/17-5/28. Check my stories for more from this session 🔋💡#performixpartner #sstenergyseltzer
